{
  "title": "Rich & Velvety British Orange Stir-fry",
  "description": "A rich and velvety British orange stir-fry featuring candied peel for added depth of flavor. Perfect as a weeknight dinner that's Mediterranean-friendly and easy to prepare.",
  "cuisine": "British",
  "diet": [
